error_message: Internal Server Error: /contact - Server error, page could not be loaded. This error was caused by an unexpected issue on the server side and an error message was shown to the user.
Internal Server Error: /api/data - Data provision error, server did not respond. An error occurred during the API call and data could not be provided to the user.
Internal Server Error: /contact - Recurring server error, page could not be loaded. Same cause as the previous error, an error message was shown to the user.
Unauthorized: /login - Authentication error, login failed. The user could not log in with the provided credentials.
Not Found: /submit - Page not found, no information provided to the user. The page requested by the user does not exist, an error message was shown.
Not Found: /about - Requested page does not exist, an error message was shown to the user. Page not found and error information was provided to the user.
OK: /home - Page successfully loaded. The requested data was successfully provided to the user.
Not Found: /oldpage - Old page, not found. The old page the user attempted to access does not exist, an error message was shown.
OK: /contact - Page successfully loaded, all data was provided. Accurate information was provided to the user.
